videos.description: North Carolina's Theo Pinson catches the lob from Isaiah Hicks for the first bucket of the game against Virginia.
videos.headline: UNC opens scoring with alley-oop

videos.description: North Carolina's Theo Pinson makes the layup before Justin Jackson makes the corner 3-pointer to extend Tar Heels early lead over Virginia.
videos.headline: UNC scoring in multiple ways to start game

videos.description: North Carolina's Justin Jackson makes the and-1 layup to increase his team's lead over Virginia.
videos.headline: Jackson stays hot in first half for UNC

videos.description: North Carolina's Justin Jackson finds Isaiah Hicks for the dunk as the Tar Heels lead Virginia in the first half.
videos.headline: UNC's Hicks rattles the rim with huge dunk

videos.description: Justin Jackson scores on the drive to the basket, extending North Carolina's lead over Virginia.
videos.headline: Jackson caps off huge first half with layup

videos.description: North Carolina's Tony Bradley blocks the shot attempt as the Tar Heels maintain a big lead over Virginia.
videos.headline: UNC's Bradley swats shot attempt

videos.description: North Carolina's Justin Jackson finds Isaiah Hicks in transition for the dunk, extending the Tar Heels large lead over Virginia.
videos.headline: UNC transition dunk leaves kid in awe
